		<title>17PRIVATE SCHL, NEWTON MEARNS</title>
		<content>      There is one private school in   
 the area - Belmont - which caters for 
 boys only. There is a pre-school year 
 at age 4 and a relatively large       
 Primary school. After primary many of 
 the boys leave to go to larger private
 secondary schools such as Hutcheson's 
 or boarding schools such as           
 Glenalmond. Some pupils do however    
 remain at Belmont and complete their  
 secondary education there.            
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
